commit.message: CI: use libpeas1 dependency for fedora39
tx: fix warning in Serbian translations
tx: fix warning in Japanese translations
Remove help images that are not readable

Fix building with ImageMagick 7

Check for ImageMagick 7 first, then for ImageMagick 6. Original (the
reversed) ordering might lead accidentially to HAVE_IMAGEMAGICK6 with
ImageMagick 7.
